# Intro to Front-End Apps #

Tic Tac Toe
- play against another person or computer
- if computer set its turn to random not taken spot on the board
- set end conditions
- turns ( cant go twice in a row)
- board grid
- can't replace x with o; cant remove a turn

- think about which languages would be best for each step
- think about your goals

reasons for html
- simple
- draw board in html **
- can make boxes and float and sort them
- or you can use a table

reasons for js
- testing js is easier/better?
